data.description: Welcome to this lovely three-bedroom colonial situated in a delightful residential neighborhood! On the first floor, you'll find a spacious open floor plan featuring a large living room, kitchen, dining area, and a convenient half bath. Moving up to the second floor, you'll discover three cozy bedrooms, a full bathroom, and ample closet space for all your storage needs. The basement is expansive and finished, offering plenty of room for your storage requirements and extra living space. Step outside to the fenced backyard, complete with a covered patio and a shed, perfect for enjoying outdoor activities. This property is conveniently located near schools, transportation, and shopping, making it incredibly convenient for daily life.
